completion_data.completion_summary: Team implementation v003 completed 4 phases: (1) Boundary extension infrastructure with no-sorry extendFamilyAtBoundary, (2) Restructured maximal_implies_total using boundary extension, (3) Boundary seed consistency eliminating cross-sign case, (4) F/P recovery with isolated sorry lemmas.
